# React Component Patterns

## Component Structure

- Use functional components with hooks
- Prefer `useRef` for DOM nodes, GSAP targets, and mutable values
- Use `clsx` for conditional class names

## GSAP Usage

- Register plugins at component level: `gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger, ScrollToPlugin)`
- Use `gsap.context()` in `useEffect` and return `ctx.revert()` in cleanup to avoid leaks
- Kill tweens on unmount: `gsap.killTweensOf(ref.current)` when needed

## Form & State

- Contact form: multi-step with `formSteps` array; `fullName` split into `firstName`/`lastName` for API
- Avoid interpolating raw user input into HTML — sanitize for XSS (see CODEBASE_ANALYSIS.md)

## Internationalization

- Use `useLanguage()` from `@/context/LanguageContext`
- Keys: `TranslationKey` type; add new keys in both `tr` and `en` in `LanguageContext.tsx`

## Section Components

- Wrap in `SectionWrapper` with `id` matching `SECTIONS`
- Use `overflowVisible` prop when 3D perspective / tilt effects need to overflow
